title: Philo Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. It serves meat, and vegetarian and vegan options are available. The dishes of the day are announced weekly on their Facebook page and hang out near the entrance. They also offer sandwiches and pastries. Vegetarian and vegan choices are labelled.
